            Game Instructions

New game will launch you to a menu to choose your starting options.

You do not have to select any specific options as there are defaults.

Each room will have doors in it.These doors are locked with trivia questions.

There is 3 types of questions you will have to answer:
True/false, Multiple Choice, Short Answer.

In order to traverse the maze you will have to choose a direction, you can go to rooms
previously visited by clicking on the corresponding direction button.

After you have answered the question click on the submit button.
                View:
Doors are displayed in yellow.
Undiscovered rooms are dark purple.
Discovered rooms are black.

There are 4 different directions you can move these are:
north, south, east, west

The directions buttons can only be selected if there is
a room in the corresponding direction.






